{"title":"docker提示没有权限，Got permission denied while trying to connect to the Docker daemon socket at unix____va","date":"2023-07-28T17:40:19.053Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2023年7月28日","L":"2023/07/28","MM-DD":"07-28"},"link":"2023/07/28/docker提示没有权限，Got permission denied while trying to connect to the Docker daemon socket at unix____va","updated":"2023-07-28T08:57:58.675Z","content":"<p>依次执行下面三行代码</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#创建docker用户组</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo groupadd docker </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#把当前登陆用户添加进docker组</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo gpasswd -a 你的账户名 docker </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#更新docker用户组列表</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">newgrp docker</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>Ps:如果还是不行可以尝试注销用户重新登陆，或者重启系统！</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/65c5ca06d06d4613a0a1a7213a4b0039.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n","prev":{"title":"docker常用命令","link":"2023/07/28/docker常用命令"},"next":{"title":"docker部署minio","link":"2023/07/28/docker部署minio"},"plink":"http://glj520.tk/2023/07/28/docker提示没有权限，Got permission denied while trying to connect to the Docker daemon socket at unix____va/","reading_time":"108 字约 1 分钟"}